dma-hdma_ff55_countdown_ss-cgb|cgb|mooneye|test-roms/build/dma/hdma_ff55_countdown_ss.cgb.mooneye.gbc
ppu-window_scx_ignore-dmg|dmg|png|test-roms/build/ppu/window_scx_ignore.dmg.png.gb|test-roms/refs/ppu/window_scx_ignore.dmg.png
